HEADWORD: Stahlian
<hw>Stahl"ian</hw> <pr>(st⟦aum⟧l"y⟦ait⟧n)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Pertaining to, or taught by, <persfn><etsep>Stahl</etsep></persfn>,
a German physician and chemist of the 17th century; <as>as, the
<ex>Stahlian</ex> theory of phlogiston</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stahlian</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Stahlian
<hw>Stahl"ian</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A believer in, or advocate of,
Stahlism.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stahlianism</ent>⟦br⟧
